{"chapter_number":84,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":83,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"الإنشقاق","name_complex":"Al-'Inshiqāq","name_simple":"Al-Inshiqaq","verses_count":25,"pages":[589,589],"meaning":{"text":"The Sundering","en":"The Sundering","id":"Terbelah"},"verses":[[[1,5885,"84:1","إِذَا السَّمَاءُ انشَقَّتْ",["When the heaven bursts asunder,","Apabila langit terbelah,"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[2,5886,"84:2","وَأَذِنَتْ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتْ",["And obeys its Lord and it must.","dan patuh kepada Tuhannya, dan sudah semestinya patuh,"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[3,5887,"84:3","وَإِذَا الْأَرْضُ مُدَّتْ",["And when the earth is stretched,","dan apabila bumi diratakan,"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[4,5888,"84:4","وَأَلْقَتْ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتْ",["And casts forth what is in it and becomes empty,","dan memuntahkan apa yang ada di dalamnya dan menjadi kosong,"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[5,5889,"84:5","وَأَذِنَتْ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتْ",["And obeys its Lord and it must.","dan patuh kepada Tuhannya, dan sudah semestinya patuh."],589,30,59,236,null,null],[6,5890,"84:6","يَا أَيُّهَا الْإِنسَانُ إِنَّكَ كَادِحٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ كَدْحًا فَمُلَاقِيهِ",["O man! surely you must strive (to attain) to your Lord, a hard striving until you meet Him.","Wahai manusia! Sesungguhnya kamu telah bekerja keras menuju Tuhanmu, maka kamu akan menemui-Nya."],589,30,59,236,null,null],[7,5891,"84:7","فَأَمَّا مَنْ أُوتِيَ كِتَابَهُ بِيَمِينِهِ",["Then as to him who is given his book in his right hand,","Maka adapun orang yang catatannya diberikan dari sebelah kanannya,"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[8,5892,"84:8","فَسَوْفَ يُحَاسَبُ حِسَابًا يَسِيرًا",["He shall be reckoned with by an easy reckoning,","maka dia akan diperiksa dengan pemeriksaan yang mudah,"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[9,5893,"84:9","وَيَنقَلِبُ إِلَىٰ أَهْلِهِ مَسْرُورًا",["And he shall go back to his people joyful.","dan dia akan kembali kepada keluarganya (yang sama-sama beriman) dengan gembira."],589,30,59,236,null,null],[10,5894,"84:10","وَأَمَّا مَنْ أُوتِيَ كِتَابَهُ وَرَاءَ ظَهْرِهِ",["And as to him who is given his book behind his back,","Dan adapun orang yang catatannya diberikan dari sebelah belakang,"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[11,5895,"84:11","فَسَوْفَ يَدْعُو ثُبُورًا",["He shall call for perdition,","maka dia akan berteriak, “Celakalah aku!”"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[12,5896,"84:12","وَيَصْلَىٰ سَعِيرًا",["And enter into burning fire.","Dan dia akan masuk ke dalam api yang menyala-nyala (neraka)."],589,30,59,236,null,null],[13,5897,"84:13","إِنَّهُ كَانَ فِي أَهْلِهِ مَسْرُورًا",["Surely he was (erstwhile) joyful among his followers.","Sungguh, dia dahulu (di dunia) bergembira di kalangan keluarganya (yang sama-sama kafir)."],589,30,59,236,null,null],[14,5898,"84:14","إِنَّهُ ظَنَّ أَن لَّن يَحُورَ",["Surely he thought that he would never return.","Sesungguhnya dia mengira bahwa dia tidak akan kembali (kepada Tuhannya)."],589,30,59,236,null,null],[15,5899,"84:15","بَلَىٰ إِنَّ رَبَّهُ كَانَ بِهِ بَصِيرًا",["Yea! surely his Lord does ever see him.","Tidak demikian, sesungguhnya Tuhannya selalu melihatnya."],589,30,59,236,null,null],[16,5900,"84:16","فَلَا أُقْسِمُ بِالشَّفَقِ",["But nay! I swear by the sunset redness,","Maka Aku bersumpah demi cahaya merah pada waktu senja,"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[17,5901,"84:17","وَاللَّيْلِ وَمَا وَسَقَ",["And the night and that which it drives on,","demi malam dan apa yang diselubunginya,"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[18,5902,"84:18","وَالْقَمَرِ إِذَا اتَّسَقَ",["And the moon when it grows full,","demi bulan apabila jadi purnama,"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[19,5903,"84:19","لَتَرْكَبُنَّ طَبَقًا عَن طَبَقٍ",["That you shall most certainly enter one state after another.","sungguh, akan kamu jalani tingkat demi tingkat (dalam kehidupan)."],589,30,59,236,null,null],[20,5904,"84:20","فَمَا لَهُمْ لَا يُؤْمِنُونَ",["But what is the matter with them that they do not believe,","Maka mengapa mereka tidak mau beriman?"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[21,5905,"84:21","وَإِذَا قُرِئَ عَلَيْهِمُ الْقُرْآنُ لَا يَسْجُدُونَ",["And when the Quran is recited to them they do not make obeisance?","Dan apabila Al-Qur'an dibacakan kepada mereka, mereka tidak (mau) bersujud,"],589,30,59,236,"optional",13],[22,5906,"84:22","بَلِ الَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا يُكَذِّبُونَ",["Nay! those who disbelieve give the lie to the truth.","bahkan orang-orang kafir itu mendustakan(nya)."],589,30,59,236,null,null],[23,5907,"84:23","وَاللَّهُ أَعْلَمُ بِمَا يُوعُونَ",["And Allah knows best what they hide,","Dan Allah lebih mengetahui apa yang mereka sembunyikan (dalam hati mereka)."],589,30,59,236,null,null],[24,5908,"84:24","فَبَشِّرْهُم بِعَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍ",["So announce to them a painful punishment~","Maka sampaikanlah kepada mereka (ancaman) azab yang pedih,"],589,30,59,236,null,null],[25,5909,"84:25","إِلَّا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحَاتِ لَهُمْ أَجْرٌ غَيْرُ مَمْنُونٍ",["Except those who believe and do good; for them is a reward that shall never be cut off.","kecuali orang-orang yang beriman dan mengerjakan kebajikan, mereka akan mendapat pahala yang tidak putus-putusnya."],589,30,59,236,null,null]],[[[1,4,589,"&#xfb5c;","word","إِذَا",["When",""]],[2,4,589,"&#xfb5d;","word","السَّمَاءُ",["the sky",""]],[3,4,589,"&#xfb5e;","word","انْشَقَّتْ",["is split asunder",""]],[4,4,589,"&#xfb5f;","end","ﭟ",[null,null]]],[[1,4,589,"&#xfb60;","word","وَأَذِنَتْ",["And has listened","dan ia patuh"]],[2,4,589,"&#xfb61;","word","لِرَبِّهَا",["to its Lord","kepada Tuhannya"]],[3,4,589,"&#xfb62;","word","وَحُقَّتْ",["and was obligated","dan ia semestinya"]],[4,4,589,"&#xfb63;","end","ﭣ",[null,null]]],[[1,4,589,"&#xfb64;","word","وَإِذَا",["And when","dan apabila"]],[2,4,589,"&#xfb65;","word","الْأَرْضُ",["the earth","bumi"]],[3,4,589,"&#xfb66;","word","مُدَّتْ",["is spread","dipanjangkan/diratakan"]],[4,5,589,"&#xfb67;","end","ﭧ",[null,null]]],[[1,5,589,"&#xfb68;","word","وَأَلْقَتْ",["And has cast out","dan ia melemparkan"]],[2,5